rows.label: tlk70000019_02_msg0001
rows.name:
When I heard that Felt'd been
attacked, my first thought was that
it wasn't anything to do with me.

rows.label: tlk70000019_02_msg0002
rows.name:
It really struck me how heartless you
can be, you know? I was just happy it
wasn't MY home getting wrecked.

rows.label: tlk70000019_02_msg0003
rows.name:
But I'm different now. I'm
not going to be thoughtless
like that anymore.

rows.label: tlk70000019_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Speaking of which! My thoughtless
oaf of a husband went out fishing
again and hasn't come home.

rows.label: tlk70000019_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Oooh, when he comes home
this time I'm going to give
him SUCH a talking to...
